org.orgName: The District Court of the United States, Western District of Washington, Northern Division

div1.p: In the District Court of the United States for the Western District of Washington.
In the Matter of the Application of Moy Share Park for a Writ of Habeas Corpus.
Filed in the United States District Court
In the Matter of the Application of Moy Share Park for a Writ of Habeas Corpus
Hearing having been had in the above entitled matter after which petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus was denied, and the matter having been finally disposed of, it is hereby

ORDERED, ADJUDGED and DECREED that certain files belonging to the Department of Immigration that were introduced in evidence marked Exhibit "A" be withdrawn from the files, and that they be returned to the Bureau of Immigration.
DATED this 14 day of May, A.D., 1920.
Received this day, May, 15, 1920, Exhibit "A" in above entitled case.
